      "side": 1,
      "message": "Think it makes sense to switch SkSamplingOptions{}\u0027s default values to be {linear,none}?  If we\u0027re going to have places in the code that hard code any sort of default opinion, it might feel nice for that default to be what you get from default constructing SkSamplingOptions{}, and I agree that {linear,none} are probably the best settings: never too terrible, never too expensive.\n\nOr is this a step towards plumbing explicit SkSamplingOptions through SkPictureShader too, replacing this hardcoded choice with a user parameter?",
